l come\". <i>JAMA</i>. <b>294</b> (11): 1343\u201351. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1001/jama.294.11.1343\">10.1001/jama.294.11.1343</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16174692\">16174692</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=JAMA&amp;rft.atitle=The+physician-scientist+career+pipeline+in+2005%3A+build+it%2C+and+they+will+come.&amp;rft.volume=294&amp;rft.issue=11&amp;rft.pages=1343-51&amp;rft.date=2005-09-21&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1001%2Fjama.294.11.1343&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F16174692&amp;rft.aulast=Ley&amp;rft.aufirst=TJ&amp;rft.au=Rosenberg%2C+LE&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APhysician-scientist\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-nih-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-nih_3-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-nih_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-nih_3-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-nih_3-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://report.nih.gov/workforce/psw/index.aspx\">\"Physician-Scientist Workforce (PSW) Report 2014\"</a>. <i>NIH RePORT</i>. National Institutes of Health<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">12 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=NIH+RePORT&amp;rft.atitle=Physician-Scientist+Workforce+%28PSW%29+Report+2014&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Freport.nih.gov%2Fworkforce%2Fpsw%2Findex.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APhysician-scientist\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-dophd-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-dophd_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.physicianscientists.org/?page=DOPhDProgramsList\">\"Do/PhD Programs\"</a>. <i>American Physician Scientists Association</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Physician+Scientists+Association&amp;rft.atitle=Do%2FPhD+Programs&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.physicianscientists.org%2F%3Fpage%3DDOPhDProgramsList&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APhysician-scientist\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-nih-mstp-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-nih-mstp_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nigms.nih.gov/Training/InstPredoc/Pages/PredocOverview-MSTP.aspx\">\"Medical Scientist Training Program\"</a>. <i>National Institute of General Medical Sciences</i>. National Institutes of Health<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=National+Institute+of+General+Medical+Sciences&amp;rft.atitle=Medical+Scientist+Training+Program&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nigms.nih.gov%2FTraining%2FInstPredoc%2FPages%2FPredocOverview-MSTP.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AP